      "sc:author": "Manuel Marfil-Trujillo",
      "sc:description": "This preprocessing tool is design for 2D digital mammograms in DICOM  format. It standardizes and harmonizes images through a configurable pipeline that includes spatial reorientation, pseudo-3D stacking, isotropic resampling, intensity normalization, optional denoising, contrast enhancement, and mask processing (if available).",
